Package demo.projects.test.framework.driver.abstraction

Class DriverWrapper

java.lang.Object
demo.projects.test.framework.driver.abstraction.DriverWrapper
Direct Known Subclasses:
AndroidApp, AndroidBrowser, Browser
public abstract class DriverWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
Abstract Wrapper class for Selenium driver. To be extended by other classes implementing concrete drivers.

    • defaultWaitValue

      @Value("${defaultWait}") protected int defaultWaitValue
      Integer value of defaultWait timeout in seconds. Can be used in other calls for default timeout, where WebDriverWait is not used.

      public void getScreenshot​(java.lang.String filePathToSaveScreenshotTo)
